#: content/templates/main/about.html:7
msgid "About StoneWalker"
msgstr "Tutto su StoneWalker"

#: content/templates/main/about.html:14
msgid ""
"StoneWalker is a unique platform that combines the joy of geocaching with "
"the beauty of collaborative art. Our mission is to create a global community"
" of stone travelers who paint, hide, and track beautiful stones as they "
"journey around the world."
msgstr ""

#: content/templates/main/about.html:20
msgid "Did you know:"
msgstr "Lo sapevi che:"

#: content/templates/main/about.html:20
msgid ""
"One of the oldest known cave paintings, found in Indonesia, is over 45,000 "
"years old. This shows that humans have always been drawn to creating art in "
"unexpected places."
msgstr ""

#: content/templates/main/about.html:24
msgid "Read more about this discovery →"
msgstr "Leggi di più su questa scoperta fantastica →"

#: content/templates/main/about.html:32
msgid "How it works:"
msgstr "Come funziona:"

#: content/templates/main/about.html:35
msgid "Pick up a brush and paint a stone."
msgstr "Prendi un pennello e dipingi un sasso!"

#: content/templates/main/about.html:39
msgid "Click the \"Create a Stone\" button and follow the instructions."
msgstr "Clicca il pulsante \"Crea una pietra\" e segui le istruzioni."

#: content/templates/main/about.html:43
msgid "Glue the custom QR code on the back of the stone."
msgstr "Incolla il codice QR speciale sul retro del sasso."

#: content/templates/main/about.html:47
msgid "Set it free and watch it travel the world."
msgstr "Liberalo e guardalo viaggiare per il mondo!"

#: content/templates/main/about.html:54
msgid "Community Guidelines:"
msgstr "Regole della Comunità:"

#: content/templates/main/about.html:55
msgid "Use non-toxic, weather-resistant paint, like acrylic."
msgstr "Usa colori non tossici e resistenti al tempo, come quelli acrilici."

#: content/templates/main/about.html:56 content/templates/main/about.html:58
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Don\\\\\\\\"
msgid "Don\\"
msgstr "Non"

#: content/templates/main/about.html:57
msgid "Be kind and respectful to other community members!"
msgstr "Sii gentile e rispettoso con gli altri membri della comunità!"

#: content/templates/main/about.html:60
msgid ""
"You never know where it might go, or who it might inspire along the way!"
msgstr "Non si sa mai dove andrà o chi potrebbe ispirare lungo il cammino!"

#: content/templates/main/about.html:66
msgid "Start Your Journey"
msgstr "Inizia la Tua Avventura"

#: content/templates/main/change_language.html:20
msgid "Select your preferred language"
msgstr "Scegli la tua lingua preferita"

